Extend build.rs to validate inlines.scm captures at build time. Required captures (inline.definition, def_name, body, call, call_name) missing -> warning, inlining disabled for that language. Partial capture groups -> warning. Syntax error -> build error. Generate InlineCapabilities struct (has_substitution, has_imports, has_returns) embedded in LanguageInfo. Per-language validation: broken inlines.scm for one language does not block others. See spec "Build-Time Diagnostics".
